WEBVTT

00:00:00.476 --> 00:00:02.500
Track 10.06

00:00:04.412 --> 00:00:06.067
A: Oh, excuse me!

00:00:06.646 --> 00:00:09.411
B: Yes? How can I help?

00:00:09.866 --> 00:00:12.770
A: What time’s the next bus to Seville?

00:00:13.347 --> 00:00:16.249
B: It’s at quarter past eleven.

00:00:16.578 --> 00:00:19.809
A: So it leaves in ten minutes.

00:00:20.122 --> 00:00:21.743
Is it a direct bus?

00:00:22.016 --> 00:00:25.280
B: No, you change at Córdoba.

00:00:25.663 --> 00:00:28.259
A: OK, and which bus stop is it?

00:00:28.577 --> 00:00:31.950
B: Number 2, near the ticket office.

00:00:32.166 --> 00:00:34.365
A: Great! Thanks for your help.

00:00:34.751 --> 00:00:36.043
B: No problem.